summary: The report summarizes information from various sources, including a former Panamanian Charge d'Affaires, regarding medical aid to Cuba, Cuban medical personnel, and related matters, with attachments providing supporting details.
summary_one_paragraph: This confidential report, dated October 23, 1963, compiles information from various sources, including a former Panamanian Charge in Habana regarding medicine shipments to Cuba and data obtained by ASSET. It includes a bulletin from the Frente Interna Anti-Comunista, a letter concerning the purchase of film from Czechoslovakia for Cuban scientific institutions, a debriefing of a medical student, a commentary by a Cuban medical leader, and a listing of medical personnel in Habana with possible communist affiliations, received via diplomatic pouch.
title: MRSAVE Report
